{"tid":1285240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地唔好再死，香港需要更多香港人同膠POST","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:28:11.000Z","uid":32355,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35455c38340de4f501023bd47ffb5f7ea77462c7","tid":1285240,"uid":32355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你地，唔好再死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知道大家可能壓力好大<br />\n我明白未來可能睇唔到曙光<br />\n但點都好，唔好死!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去下旅行，睇下IG或者舊POST<br />\n你會發現喱個香港政權根本係好細好細而且好垃圾<br />\n為咁而死，<span style=\"color: red;\">值得咩</span>?<br />\n我地努力左咁耐，林鄭個八婆都係冇正面回應<br />\n就咁認輸，<span style=\"color: red;\">你甘心咩</span>?<br />\n<br />\n大陸有心溝淡我地香港人<br />\n我地就更加<span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能少</span>!<br />\n唔好再話以死鳴志<br />\n我幾肯定就算200萬人一齊跳樓個政府都係繼續等中共落ORDER先做野<br />\n相反<br />\n留住有用之軀<br />\n和理非 &gt; 勇武 &gt; 死線 &gt; 升級 &gt; 和理非......<br />\n總有一日連中共都要跪低<br />\n到時希望你地都會係到<br />\n個世界已經認同我地<br />\n未來亦係屬於大家，無論幾辛苦都要頂落去!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為香港人係<span style=\"color: red;\">從來都唔會認輸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頂唔順嘅<br />\n去個旅行散一散心 (最多幫你PLAN埋行程)<br />\n食野又好睇外國IG都好<br />\n做下一時嘅港豬唔再係罪<br />\n有需要嘅時候企出去，第二日照樣吃喝玩樂做港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係頂唔順嘅遠離電話同上網<br />\n做下運動/行山/搭下叮叮，你會發現香港依舊美麗<br />\n仆街嘅只係極少數人同個政府<br />\n仲差幾步我地就贏，等多一陣啦好嗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">撚撚FACE</span>呢? <span style=\"color: red;\">夫子</span>呢?<br />\n我知道大家可能連出POST嘅心情/時間都冇<br />\n但今次係成個連登需要你地<br />\n自認創意台台主嘅大家麻煩出POST啦好嗎?<br />\n膠POST教世界嘅時候到<br />\n負能量/計劃留返係喱到時事台<br />\n希望大家每睇半個鐘時事, 上返10分鐘創意台輕鬆下<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n唔好跌落去呀!!!!!!"},{"pid":"4756d81b342e1eb9b293101ea3556b2fdae4565e","tid":1285240,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2800cd7b32364d44caa8d5b78ab0d308dfd7e2ed","tid":1285240,"uid":32355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4756d81b342e1eb9b293101ea3556b2fdae4565e","tid":1285240,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"無事則隱，有事則隱<br />\n頂唔順嘅就訓一陣<br />\n等7月7先覺醒啦<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"d1ca67e047c7602e9b2ee063036e327a139adfd0","tid":1285240,"uid":32355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2800cd7b32364d44caa8d5b78ab0d308dfd7e2ed","tid":1285240,"uid":32355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4756d81b342e1eb9b293101ea3556b2fdae4565e","tid":1285240,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"無事則隱，有事則隱<br />\n頂唔順嘅就訓一陣<br />\n等7月7先覺醒啦<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019